{"@context":"http://iiif.io/api/presentation/3/context.json","id":"https://digbmc.github.io/pta-manifests/phan/phan-20144/manifest.json","type":"Manifest","label":{"none":["PHAN-20144"]},"metadata":[{"label":{"none":["Timestamp"]},"value":{"none":["2:01:44"]}},{"label":{"none":["Film"]},"value":{"none":["Phantom Thread"]}},{"label":{"none":["Distance"]},"value":{"none":["close-up"]}},{"label":{"none":["Angle"]},"value":{"none":["low"]}},{"label":{"none":["Location"]},"value":{"none":["interior"]}},{"label":{"none":["Movement"]},"value":{"none":["mobile, handheld"]}},{"label":{"none":["Lighting"]},"value":{"none":["low key"]}},{"label":{"none":["Composition"]},"value":{"none":["two shot"]}}],"summary":{"none":["A man gets his mouth checked by a doctor."]},"thumbnail":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-20144/tiles/full/300,169/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":169,"width":300}],"homepage":[{"id":"PHAN-20144","type":"Text","format":"text/html","label":{"none":["Object homepage"]}}],"items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-20144/canvas/1","type":"Canvas","height":1080,"width":1920,"label":{"none":["PHAN-20144"]},"thumbnail":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-20144/tiles/full/300,169/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":169,"width":300}],"items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-20144/canvas/1/annopage-1","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-20144/canvas/1/annopage-1/anno-1","type":"Annotation","motivation":"painting","target":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-20144/canvas/1","body":{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-20144/tiles/full/1920,1080/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":1080,"width":1920,"service":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-20144/tiles","type":"ImageService3","profile":"http://iiif.io/api/image/3/level0.json"}]}}]}],"annotations":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-20144/canvas/1/page/p1","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-20144/canvas/1/76cd638c-48bd-450c-9a80-b43619116c3e","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":[{"created":"2026-06-29T14:54:05.134Z","creator":"Ada ","purpose":"commenting","type":"TextualBody","format":"text/html","value":"<p>According to production designer Mark Tildesley, Daniel Day-Lewis required that the color of Reynolds’s bedroom wall be changed before shooting began in Owlpen Manor (“About the Production,” 24).&nbsp;</p>"}],"target":{"type":"SpecificResource","source":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-20144/canvas/1","selector":{"type":"FragmentSelector","conformsTo":"http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/","value":"xywh=pixel:1440.244467703349,129.3211722488038,285.80517344497616,162.81549043062196"}}},{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-20144/canvas/1/2d992d4b-60f2-41a8-bd7b-58d313b7e252","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":[{"created":"2026-06-29T14:54:28.136Z","creator":"Ada ","purpose":"commenting","type":"TextualBody","format":"text/html","value":"<p>This moment literalizes the film’s attempts to make sense of its protagonists’ inner states. Much as Dr. Hardy peers into Reynold’s throat, we, too, as viewers try to make sense of what’s going on inside their minds when they behave so strangely. This shot likewise emphasizes the film’s dry, if vomit-filled humor.&nbsp;</p>"}],"target":{"type":"SpecificResource","source":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-20144/canvas/1","selector":{"type":"FragmentSelector","conformsTo":"http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/","value":"xywh=pixel:686.5146531100478,458.1616327751196,550.6780801435406,459.24491626794253"}}}]}]}]}